trans-unit.source: The execution environment of the activity handling the callback.
trans-unit.target: O ambiente de execução da atividade que trata o retorno de chamada.

trans-unit.source: The completed activity instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" /> handler.
trans-unit.target: A instância de atividade concluída do manipulador de <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" />.

trans-unit.source: The output arguments of the completed <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" />.
trans-unit.target: Os argumentos de saída do <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" /> concluído.

trans-unit.source: Represents the method that is called when an <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" /> completes.
trans-unit.target: Representa o método que é chamado quando um <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate" /> é concluído.

trans-unit.source: The values in the `outArguments` dictionary are the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter> values of the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> that are assigned when the <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> is invoked, keyed by <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter.Name%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Os valores a `outArguments` dicionário são o <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter> valores do <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> que são atribuídos quando o <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegate> é invocado, organizado pela <xref:System.Activities.ActivityDelegateParameter.Name%2A>.
